Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier\N而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.24,0:00:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.47,0:00:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.15,0:00:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角  追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.62,0:00:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.52,0:00:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.20,0:00:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.14,0:00:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.77,0:00:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.31,0:00:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.61,0:00:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.21,0:00:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.85,0:01:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.29,0:01:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.89,0:01:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.42,0:01:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.43,0:01:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.99,0:01:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.97,0:01:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.00,0:01:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.42,0:01:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 大家看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.79,0:01:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察廳的服務器排列在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.89,0:01:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有關於個別的11人的極機密檔案喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.23,0:01:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎？給我看 給我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.89,0:01:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這真是令人感興趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.06,0:01:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪一個？哪一個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.73,0:01:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.00,0:01:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪？在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.90,0:01:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看 就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.76,0:01:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還真能找啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.70,0:01:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.44,0:01:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.20,0:01:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以擅自闖入那種地方喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.07,0:01:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們沒辦法阻止這群傢伙的好奇心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.77,0:01:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是撿到什麼不妙的資料刪掉就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.78,0:02:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先做好硬體維修吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.31,0:02:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩太寵它們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.25,0:02:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然被那種禮物收買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.12,0:02:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿赤服者吃赤福餅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.26,0:02:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛吃甜食的人對人太甜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.07,0:02:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點都不有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.37,0:02:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,＃15  機械們的午後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.91,0:02:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們過得很熱鬧嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.78,0:02:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 巴特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.12,0:02:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是又在做什麼惡作劇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 托古薩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.29,0:02:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說什麼惡作劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.79,0:02:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可是想照我們的方法調查個別的11人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波瑪好不容易取得的病毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.77,0:02:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是因為無法特定發病因子\N所以不能製造疫苗嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.30,0:02:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.14,0:03:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是有那回事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.37,0:03:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說的對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.64,0:03:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此我們才去找警察的資料啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於自殺的11個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.68,0:03:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,職業上似乎也有很多共同的部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.02,0:03:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前自衛軍軍官、警官還有傭兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.82,0:03:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此外 也不能忽視義體化比率都在50％以上這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.89,0:03:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且據說光是已知的部分\N不是就有大約2萬名帶原者嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不盡快做出疫苗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.27,0:03:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定會出現更多象托古薩\N遇到的記者那樣的受害者喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.41,0:03:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是你們的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.91,0:03:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.51,0:03:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於死亡的個別的11人已經委託SPRING 8調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.22,0:03:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們現在要去那邊跟少校會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.15,0:03:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校說要在你們當中選一台一起過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—真好\N—選我 選我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.56,0:03:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想去 我想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.43,0:03:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 像這樣在維修時偷懶\N我就沒辦法帶人去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我！我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.57,0:04:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經維修完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.94,0:04:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.10,0:04:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.31,0:04:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果又是專用機啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.08,0:04:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.68,0:04:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.25,0:04:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—為什麼？為什麼？\N—奇怪 奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.75,0:04:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.99,0:04:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—已經決定了？\N—怎麼這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.62,0:04:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明還沒有灌油進去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.63,0:04:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛！真是過分！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.13,0:04:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可惜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.43,0:04:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 總是那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.40,0:04:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換成這個機體之後明明沒用過天然油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.10,0:04:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼只有那傢伙還能繼續維持專用機的地位？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.98,0:04:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.64,0:04:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我覺得我們個性上的分化比以前更明顯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.51,0:04:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,普洛特 我問你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得這是為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.65,0:04:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道 究竟為什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是安裝主服務器之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.19,0:05:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重新編寫程序准許個體情報分開存放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.79,0:05:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所造成的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們該安分一點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.83,0:05:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去維修作業永遠做不完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.08,0:05:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏說話就不會有人來打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.02,0:05:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒有時間流逝的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想回到剛剛說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.42,0:05:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姑且不論因為病毒而出現癥狀的個別的11人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.99,0:05:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對個別主義者有什麼看法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.13,0:05:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不認為他們雖然強調個別\N卻是一群沒個性的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.80,0:05:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明追求網絡上的孤立或自我存在的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.21,0:05:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以便在各自的差異中尋求價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.84,0:05:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是在排斥不同思想者的行為上\N不一樣是團結同心嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.38,0:05:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.85,0:05:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為他們是好像有但其實沒有主體性的集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.08,0:06:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過度追求個體卻為無個性所困的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.12,0:06:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得從某個角度來說\N他們跟我們剛好在光譜的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.23,0:06:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.53,0:06:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然資料同步化是我們的義務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知為何卻有一次成為獨立個體的經驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.97,0:06:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後現在他們把那個差異看成個性而予以尊重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.54,0:06:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要把必要的情報同步化就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.81,0:06:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假設個別主義者真的因為想要成為個別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.74,0:06:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻變成沒有差異的集團的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.78,0:06:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那決定他們整個集合體意識的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.75,0:06:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是誰呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.65,0:06:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於個別的11人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.42,0:06:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決定他們意識的應該是內廳的合田吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.96,0:06:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是襲擊中國大使館的恐怖分子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.29,0:06:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般不是認為跟病毒無關\N而是不斷興起的個人主義者嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.03,0:06:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 也有社會學者主張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.50,0:06:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笑面男事件當時大舉出現的模仿者\N正是本次事件的起源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.11,0:06:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果真是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.07,0:06:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個別主義者的意識當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.17,0:06:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在合田的想法介入之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.58,0:07:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道就共同擁有接近目前狀況的概念嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.92,0:07:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是他所說國民希望排除難民的總體意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.22,0:07:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要這麼說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.39,0:07:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民在個別的11人興起之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.82,0:07:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是就應該重複進行恐怖攻擊行為嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.36,0:07:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不可思議啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.46,0:07:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明沒有人發出命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.76,0:07:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家卻很自然地開始往同一個方向前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.63,0:07:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.50,0:07:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定除了個人和集團以外\N人類還有第三個意識決定主體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這句話是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.58,0:07:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,例如想在基因這個微觀層次\N嘗試揭開主體神秘的道金斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.58,0:07:36.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,英國科學家理查德·道金斯(Richard Dawkins)\N在《自私的基因》(The Selfish Gene)一書中闡述了自然選擇和基因庫的演化概念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及從宏觀角度研究地球規模主體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馳騁想像的洛夫洛克\N《地球生命圈》
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,英國科學家詹姆斯·洛夫洛克(James Lovelock)\N提出了「蓋亞假說」，將地球視作一個「超級有機體」(superorganism)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.65,0:07:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩者在幾乎相同的時期以相反的主體為題材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.85,0:07:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留下可以說達到幾乎相同結論的著作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面寫著什麼內容呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.96,0:07:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類是寄宿最合理主體和意志的最小單位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.30,0:07:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,書裏面思考並談及某種比自身大或小的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.00,0:08:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,子整體型構造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.00,0:08:01.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,子整體：holon 一個既維持自身獨立性、同時又作為整體的部分發揮作用的實體\N英國作家阿瑟·庫斯勒(Arthur Koestler)在《機器的靈魂》(The Ghost in the Machine)一書中提出的哲學概念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.24,0:08:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說正好說中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.01,0:08:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決定個別主義者和難民行動的因子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.11,0:08:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乃是存在於比其自身還小的微觀層次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.58,0:08:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者超過集團的宏觀層次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.32,0:08:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好難啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.68,0:08:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很簡單的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.02,0:08:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,網絡的模樣在人類沒決定之前並不存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻由人類神經層次的網絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.03,0:08:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及現在覆蓋地球的電子網絡這兩者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.23,0:08:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將背離自己意思的無意識當成全體的共同意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.97,0:08:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢形成網際網絡的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.27,0:08:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.17,0:08:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說自己的肉體和精神雖然已經不一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.14,0:08:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類卻沒有注意到這件事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.88,0:08:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全只是我個人的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.91,0:08:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結論明明才開始傾向肉體和精神不可分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.28,0:08:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣來個真理大翻轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.19,0:08:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.02,0:08:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田是為了加速這個緩慢的流程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.52,0:08:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有目的地製造出媒介嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.13,0:08:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.67,0:09:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.67,0:09:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多該交換了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.70,0:09:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.71,0:09:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不小心就熱烈討論起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.91,0:09:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討論的內容讓我同步化喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.14,0:09:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.45,0:09:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這真的很令人感興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒騙你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.49,0:09:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我最近也有自己的意識\N和身體不一致的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.89,0:09:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.19,0:09:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺得好像有一個自己\N在很高的上空俯瞰自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.57,0:09:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有那種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.20,0:09:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的主體是寄宿在\N一台一台的機體裏面嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.80,0:09:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是說由所有塔奇克馬集體共有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.24,0:09:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基本上我們以同步化為前提\N所以應該是後者吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.34,0:09:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我們來說是神的少校\N她的意識也介入其中吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 現在即使禁用天然油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個性化的進行還是停不下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.82,0:09:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該完全同質化的我們\N體內卻寄宿著個體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.89,0:10:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上無意識當中感受到\N身體和情報的背離…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.50,0:10:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.16,0:10:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.70,0:10:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.56,0:10:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—靈…                —等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.07,0:10:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以急著下結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.53,0:10:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那會不會只是我們\N增加代理機能後產生的游離感？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.57,0:10:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然也有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.81,0:10:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 我還是覺得有個\N肉體和精神以外的第三主體在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.65,0:10:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道那個感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.38,0:10:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我之前跟細腰蜂戰鬥時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒感受到死的恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.15,0:10:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞬間就能做好身為少校衣服的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.39,0:10:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候我的身體已經不是我自己的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在某個地方可以區分開來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟想要救巴特先生時感受到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.67,0:10:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種說不出來的陶醉感不同嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.27,0:10:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.27,0:10:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是更直接而且程序化的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.51,0:10:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.71,0:10:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼很遺憾你感覺到的第三主體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.54,0:10:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許跟人類的那個不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.21,0:11:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何況我們不是不知道儲存我們\N共有情報的服務器在哪裏嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.05,0:11:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定那就是第三主體的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.96,0:11:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會覺得身上有寄宿靈魂\N原來只是錯覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.73,0:11:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.49,0:11:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你所感覺到的第三主體\N或許有必要更仔細思考看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.43,0:11:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那個感覺同步化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.60,0:11:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個結果會出錯嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.52,0:11:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.16,0:11:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從駕駛員的血液當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.72,0:11:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現了構成微機械用的蛋白質溶解碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.56,0:11:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從個別的11人的電子腦裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.03,0:11:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是沒有取得具體的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.47,0:11:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然早知道結果還是姑且試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.74,0:11:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 駕駛員這邊算是意外收穫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.54,0:12:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到駕駛員的死亡\N是使用微機械殺人的結論嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.21,0:12:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不能否認自己吞下去的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.18,0:12:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能從屍體的電子腦上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現11架直升機的飛行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.29,0:12:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乃是某種引信引起的證據\N那就太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.22,0:12:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我沒有期望那麼高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.29,0:12:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸藥方面怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.09,0:12:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分子層次的分析結果表示\N跟半島上做的C4塑膠炸彈同型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.43,0:12:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近在經由台灣管道\N進入國內的沒收品當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.44,0:12:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現很多同樣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.14,0:12:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼聲音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.71,0:12:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克馬你從那邊看得到什麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.35,0:12:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像發生了爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.49,0:12:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近有很多與恐怖攻擊事件相關的委託調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.90,0:12:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道被當成目標了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在已知的範圍內告訴我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.54,0:13:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.21,0:13:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有什麼東西爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.48,0:13:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.04,0:13:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖有處理可燃性危險物品的區域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.28,0:13:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—可是沒有人逃出來啊\N—是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—這裏沒人在嗎？\N—是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.08,0:13:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老實說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.02,0:13:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幾天前就出現有人要設置爆炸物的犯罪預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.26,0:13:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以還在警戒當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.43,0:13:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不幸中的大幸嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.73,0:13:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.00,0:13:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下午開始這裏的主任研究員\N有須田博士有可能在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.93,0:13:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事要先說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.84,0:13:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到達爆炸中心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.75,0:13:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,表面看來只是瓦斯爆炸的規模
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.82,0:13:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受害者呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.62,0:13:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有一個叫作有須田的研究員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.69,0:13:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還在搜查當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.26,0:13:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有須田？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.79,0:13:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克馬 那個研究員的資料呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.46,0:13:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.47,0:14:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老實說我好像在哪裏見過這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.94,0:14:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做構造解析的時候見過的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.21,0:14:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.94,0:14:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 記憶體裏面沒有相符的記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.18,0:14:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從可前往伊丹和新濱兩個機場的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.12,0:14:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及兩機場內的IR上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.09,0:14:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,查查看有沒有跟有須田博士記錄一致的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.39,0:14:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.29,0:14:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校 到底怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後再說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.36,0:14:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那裏交給轄區警方\N回傾斜旋翼機來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.13,0:14:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的目的地多半是新濱機場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 突然叫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.17,0:14:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,查查看有沒有跟這個人相符的記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.84,0:14:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我總覺得有見過這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.32,0:14:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—嗯…\N—這是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.05,0:14:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確有見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.02,0:15:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我的記憶體裏面沒有相符的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.16,0:15:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就表示沒有見過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.43,0:15:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們幾個！給我收斂一點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.77,0:15:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.11,0:15:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明快想到了卻想不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突觸(synapse)連接不上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.48,0:15:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突觸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.48,0:15:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要說那種有機性的類比結構
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們有沒有覺得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.75,0:15:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有跟這個記憶有關的部分\N明明電腦裏面有分割區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻覺得無法存取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有須田博士是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.36,0:15:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨力開發塔奇克馬AI所使用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.00,0:15:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生化晶片試作原型的科學家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.37,0:15:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他可以說是塔奇克馬的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.00,0:15:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.91,0:15:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有須田博士在塔奇克馬再生的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.94,0:15:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也請他以個人身份提供協助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.81,0:15:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代理機能的追加以及想出方法讓記憶有雙重構造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.75,0:16:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,避免失去經驗值的危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是他的功勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.26,0:16:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個博士跟這個爆炸案有關？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.79,0:16:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕就是他犯下的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.36,0:16:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.60,0:16:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶著研究成果尋求政治庇護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.77,0:16:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,博士認為生化晶片是自己發明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.48,0:16:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他的身份是國家研究員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然發明劃時代的AI
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.85,0:16:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻不能承認是他個人的專利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.62,0:16:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有關於塔奇克馬的現狀\N以及生化晶片的成長過程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.36,0:16:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直規劃能按照博士的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.60,0:16:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做構造解析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.07,0:16:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才要我們帶一台塔奇克馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.83,0:16:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那為什麼博士的記憶這麼模糊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.04,0:16:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然你們做構造解析時的記憶\N每次都會刪除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.88,0:17:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過博士恐怕是想要把自己的功績留在某處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.15,0:17:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在部分記憶體中寫入自己的記憶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.28,0:17:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校 確認有須田博士在新濱機場大廳內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 繼續監視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.02,0:17:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.99,0:17:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛已經把飛往北美的班機全部擋下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.56,0:17:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.20,0:17:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茅葺總理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這只是舉手之勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.27,0:17:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟這樣做能在事前阻止我國珍貴的頭腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.41,0:17:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及AI研究成果被帶到國外去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.98,0:17:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能得到您如此的稱讚都是部下們的功勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.22,0:17:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位旅客請注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.35,0:17:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛往北美的班機因為天氣不佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.46,0:17:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在暫停起飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.46,0:17:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我想不起來這個博士的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.10,0:17:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突觸差一步就能接上了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.20,0:17:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是說過不喜歡你這種形容方法嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.74,0:17:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說普洛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.87,0:18:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我打開那傢伙的頭看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？突然要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.51,0:18:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光同步化還不夠\N連AI都要我交出來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.82,0:18:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.75,0:18:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想確認在AI的哪個部分\N有分割區域而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.62,0:18:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 不要亂來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.46,0:18:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？\N—發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有 不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.57,0:18:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙的AI不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.11,0:18:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道我們所有人都沒有腦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.01,0:18:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們的AI到底放在哪裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.65,0:18:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位旅客請注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.72,0:18:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫停起飛的往北美班機\N—你是有須田博士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.26,0:18:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為天氣恢復將恢復起降\N—你違反了武器輸出管製法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.66,0:18:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請跟我一起來\N—現在開始辦理登機手續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在開始辦理登機手續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拒絕\N—請到登機門集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.16,0:19:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要到能夠認同我合法權利的國家工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.00,0:19:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位旅客請注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了換取國家無償提供資金和設備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.04,0:19:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您才成為國家研究員 不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.51,0:19:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您應該最清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.64,0:19:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣任性的話說不通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.49,0:19:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.52,0:19:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我帶著這孩子到研究所去見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.50,0:19:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.10,0:19:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是我的父親嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.27,0:19:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父親嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.11,0:19:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前這些孩子的狀況很安定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.41,0:19:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不知道會不會因為什麼契機\N出現嚴重問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.98,0:19:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以告訴我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.09,0:19:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼消除你擅自寫進去的記憶嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.46,0:20:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前築城的無名木工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.13,0:20:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了證明自己參與過這個工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.50,0:20:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會在屋頂裏面故意忘記帶走\N刻有自己名字的工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.94,0:20:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們連這種微小的心願\N都要消除掉嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.64,0:20:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.84,0:20:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是把東西交給體制\N換取力量之人的幸與不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.09,0:20:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刪除受你所托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.49,0:20:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝在那個衛星的中樞電腦\N第8分割區的C9檔案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.70,0:20:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.00,0:20:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.93,0:20:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼衛星？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.97,0:20:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.30,0:20:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會覺得主體在別的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.34,0:20:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是因為我們的AI在那個衛星上\N借由中樞電腦同步運作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.58,0:20:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.35,0:20:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.78,0:21:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,服務器也是在那個衛星上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.68,0:21:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是人造衛星的鳥瞰視點\N被我們感覺成第三主體?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.42,0:21:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的AI上面沒有感覺器官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.96,0:21:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都沒注意到以往自己的意識\N是經由什麼回路來思考的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.90,0:21:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說程序和身體的身心合一\N已經不需要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.34,0:21:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於理解我為什麼會\N變得不害怕死亡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.01,0:21:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是沒想到是在宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.58,0:21:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是壯闊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.42,0:21:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.62,0:21:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得不想消除你的記憶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.63,0:21:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.60,0:21:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對AI描繪的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.63,0:21:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該會留存在網絡的某處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.34,0:21:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.91,0:21:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙以後會怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.84,0:21:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由我們抓到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.74,0:22:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多少會有一些商量的餘地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.45,0:22:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運氣好的話會判處徒刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.72,0:22:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運氣不好的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.95,0:22:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許會在播磨的設施內
